{"tid":678134,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"好想攬住班朋友大喊一場","createTime":"2018-05-25T21:15:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-26T14:14:03.000Z","uid":59569,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"486a3774c94f6b6bace7e4c4f72cc06cda65ac2a","tid":678134,"uid":59569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T21:15:12.000Z","msg":"我平時扮下假膠都係想個氣氛輕鬆下<br />\n我唔鐘意咩都咁認真討論<br />\n我想見住大家笑住咁傾計<br />\n我可以唔出聲淨係聽你地呻<br />\n我唔介意你地拎我黎講笑<br />\n只要你地開心<br />\n我柒下又有咩所謂<br />\n<br />\n但我真係好辛苦<br />\n我試過坐喺窗邊唔夠五秒又返入黎<br />\n我好驚，<br />\n搵社工傾過<br />\n佢就話我只係一時move on 唔到<br />\n我屌<br />\n仆街含撚死喇<br />\n<br />\n有時唔到自己控制<br />\n你唔理，件事都會繼續發生<br />\n好憎自己。<br />\n<br />\n希望各位巴打健康成長<br />\n唔好咁易受人影響感情"},{"pid":"e7a30ad7c37b2c56b1733e30413f4a6eb4ab1271","tid":678134,"uid":59569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T09:10:32.000Z","msg":"點解我要係做避人個個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"239017a51382b593f0c8e3d0f520c04b1530ecc9","tid":678134,"uid":165024,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"e7a30ad7c37b2c56b1733e30413f4a6eb4ab1271","tid":678134,"uid":59569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T09:10:32.000Z","msg":"點解我要係做避人個個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T09:12:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/26/171208_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F26%2F171208_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=98cda77c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"139928c545bff72b6e281d349e110148b7e6bca5","tid":678134,"uid":59569,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,